# 2005 Prince Edward Island Scott Tournament of Hearts

The 2005 Prince Edward Island Scott Tournament of Hearts was held Jan. 21â€“26 in at the Crapaud Community Curling Club in Crapaud, Prince Edward Island. The winning team was Team Rebecca Jean MacPhee who represented Prince Edward Island, finished with a 4-7 round-robin record at the 2005 Scott Tournament of Hearts in St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador.
